H0.text: What public school did the Duke of Edinburgh and Prince Charles attend. Eton College

H1.text: What public school did the Duke of Edinburgh and Prince Charles attend. Harrow School

H2.text: What public school did the Duke of Edinburgh and Prince Charles attend. Rugby School

H3.text: What public school did the Duke of Edinburgh and Prince Charles attend. Gordonstun

A5.text: Charles subsequently attended two of his father's former schools: Cheam School in Hampshire, from 1958, followed by Gordonstoun in Moray, beginning classes there in April 1962.
